---

<Layout title="About - Yu-Jen Lin" description="AR/VR developer and UX engineer based in WA.">
  <section class="py-20 flex-grow max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full">
    
    <FadeIn client:visible className="mb-24">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight mb-8">About Me</h1>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert prose-indigo prose-xl font-light text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-none">
        <p>Hello, I am Yu-Jen Lin, a software engineer with a UX design/research mind. I worked as a full-time software engineer in a design agency in Taiwan for a couple of years where I focused on creating interactive installations for museums and exhibitions. I then trained in UX design and UX research at the University of Michigan.</p>
        
        <p>I love making stuff to create interactive installations to give people fun and unforgettable experiences. A few students and I co-founded a maker space, DOIIIT Studio, at the University of Michigan, School of Information to bring maker culture to the school. I interned at Universal Creative and later worked there full-time, creating VR exhibitions and interactive attractions.</p>
        
        <p>Currently, I am a Product Design Prototyper at Meta Platform's Reality Labs Research, returning to my original team to create innovative and immersive experiences in AR/VR. Before this, I spent a brief period as a UX Engineer Lead at Samsung Research America after an initial four-year tenure at Meta pushing future research directions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 flex gap-4">
        <a href="/assets/docs/about/Yu-Jen_Lin_Resume2024.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 hover:shadow-indigo-500/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 no-underline">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="15" y2="3"/></svg>
          Download PDF Resume
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yujenlin1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 no-underline">
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-24 md:gap-32">
      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white w-48 shrink-0">Experience</h2>
          <div class="flex-grow space-y-10">
            {experience.map((job) => (
              <div class="group">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-baseline mb-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors">
                    {job.url ? <a href={job.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">{job.name}</a> : job.name}
                  </h3>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1 md:mt-0">{job.time}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-lg text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-medium mb-4">{job.role}</div>
                <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
                  {job.description.map(desc => <li>{desc}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white w-48 shrink-0">Education</h2>
          <div class="flex-grow space-y-6">
            {education.map((edu) => (
              <div>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-baseline mb-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">{edu.name}</h3>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1 md:mt-0">{edu.time}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-lg text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-light">{edu.role}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white w-48 shrink-0">Leadership & Teaching</h2>
          <div class="flex-grow space-y-8">
            {teachingAndLeadership.map((item) => (
              <div class="group">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-baseline mb-2">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-indigo-500 transition-colors">
                    {item.url ? <a href={item.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline">{item.name}</a> : item.name}
                  </h3>
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1 md:mt-0">{item.time}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-lg text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-medium mb-4">{item.role}</div>
                <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
                  {item.description.map(desc => <li>{desc}</li>)}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white w-48 shrink-0">Skills</h2>
          <div class="flex-grow grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            {skills.map((skillGroup) => (
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">{skillGroup.category}</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  {skillGroup.items.map(item => (
                    <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">{item}</span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
